content: Hello Naveen! Welcome to the technical round of our interview process. I'm Jeyachandran, and I'll be talking to you about your skills and experiences. Can you start by telling me about your background in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning? Your resume mentions that you've graduated with a B.Tech in AI & ML from Kongu Engineering College, and you've also worked on a project about Generative AI. Can you walk me through your understanding of Generative AI and how you applied it to your project?
